在[[氣象學|氣象學]]上，'''快速增強'''（{{lang-en|Rapid intensification}}）是指某[[熱帶氣旋|熱帶氣旋]]在短時間內剧烈增強的现象。美國[[國家颶風中心|國家颶風中心]]將“快速增強”界定為熱帶氣旋的[[最大持續風速|最大持續風速]]在24小時內，增加最少30節（每小時35英哩或每小時55公里）<ref name="NHC glossary">{{cite web|title=Glossary of NHC Terms|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-04-01|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6OVedwMm5?url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml|archivedate=2014-04-01|deadurl=no|author=National Hurricane Center|date=2013-03-25}}</ref>。

==必要條件==
===外在因素===
備以下條件，才会产生快速增強的熱帶氣旋。首先，[[海面溫度|水溫]]必須非常溫暖（接近或高於30 °C，86 °F）, 同时海水必須有深度足夠到海浪无法將較冷的海水上翻到海面。其次，[[風切變|風切變]]必須微弱；當風切變強烈時，氣旋中的[[對流#大氣對流|對流]]和環流將被破壞<ref>{{cite web|url=https://weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/hurricane-patricia-factors-for-rapid-intensification-strongest-hurricane-on|title=Multiple Factors Allowed Hurricane Patricia to Rapidly Intensify|first=Linda|last=Lam|publisher=The Weather Channel|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2018-08-06|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319114152/https://weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/hurricane-patricia-factors-for-rapid-intensification-strongest-hurricane-on|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===內在因素===
通常風暴上方的[[對流層|對流層]]上層也必須存在[[反氣旋|反氣旋]]——目的是幫助極低表面壓力的發展，在風暴的[[風眼|眼牆]]裏，空氣必然會迅速上升，而上層反氣旋亦有助將這些空氣有效地引導離開氣旋<ref name="Energetics">{{cite web | author=Diana Engle | title=Hurricane Structure and Energetics | publisher=Data Discovery Hurricane Science Center | accessdate=2008-10-26 | url=http://www.newmediastudio.org/DataDiscovery/Hurr_ED_Center/Hurr_Structure_Energetics/Hurr_Struct.html |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080527094650/http://www.newmediastudio.org/DataDiscovery/Hurr_ED_Center/Hurr_Structure_Energetics/Hurr_Struct.html <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2008-05-27}}</ref>。[[熱塔|熱塔]]的發展與熱帶氣旋的快速增強有關，在不同的洋盆上的关系有所区别<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Zhuge|first1=Xiao-Yong|last2=Ming|first2=Jie|last3=Wang|first3=Yuan|title=Reassessing the Use of Inner-Core Hot Towers to Predict Tropical Cyclone Rapid Intensification*|journal=Weather and Forecasting|date=October 2015|volume=30|issue=5|pages=1265–1279|doi=10.1175/WAF-D-15-0024.1|bibcode=2015WtFor..30.1265Z}}</ref>。

==此前的術語和定義==
美國國家颶風中心曾将“熱帶氣旋的最低氣壓在24小時內降低{{convert|42|mbar|inHg|sigfig=4}}”定义为「快速深化」（{{lang-en|Rapid deepening}}）<ref name="NHC/TPC glossary">{{cite web|title=Glossary of NHC/TPC Terms|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml|publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service|accessdate=2014-04-01|archivedate=2005-10-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051017214734/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml|author=National Hurricane Center/Tropical Prediction Center|deadurl=no|date=2005-02-07}}</ref>。现在的“快速增強”定義取代了此定义，定义為“熱帶氣旋的最大持續風速在24小時內增加最少{{convert|30|kn|mph km/h|round=5}}”<ref name="NHC glossary"/>。

